                        </div>
                        <div class="col-8 flex-grow-1">
                            <h5 class="card-title"><strong>Content Creation</strong></h5>
                            <p class="card-text"><strong>Learn how to use AI to create engaging content for your business.</strong></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 mx-2">
                        <div class="progress">
                            <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 60%;" aria-valuenow="60"
                                aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">60%</div>
